ontainer\">\n      <div class=\"zhaizhai-back-header\"><span class=\"zhaizhai-back-title\">思考卡片</span></div>\n      <div class=\"zhaizhai-back-body\"><section class=\"zhaizhai-back-section zhaizhai-back-empty\">暂无 insight</section></div>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"shuoshuo-item zhaizhai-item \">\n  <div class=\"zhaizhai-flip-card\">\n    <div class=\"zhaizhai-face zhaizhai-face-front container\">\n      <div class=\"zhaizhai-top\">\n        <div class=\"zhaizhai-tags\"></div>\n        <time class=\"zhaizhai-date\">2022-02-11</time>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"zhaizhai-content-wrap\">\n        <div class=\"zhaizhai-content\">姜女不尚铅华，<br>似疏梅之映淡月；<br>禅师不落空寂，<br>若碧沼之吐青莲。</div>\n        <div class=\"zhaizhai-source\">—— 节选自《菜根谭》</div>\n        <div class=\"zhaizhai-meta\">\n          <span></span>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"zhaizhai-face zhaizhai-face-back container\">\n      <div class=\"zhaizhai-back-header\"><span class=\"zhaizhai-back-title\">思考卡片</span></div>\n      <div class=\"zhaizhai-back-body\"><section class=\"zhaizhai-back-section zhaizhai-back-empty\">暂无 insight</section></div>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<script>\n(() => {\n  let flipSwitchTimer = null\n\n  document.addEventListener('click', event => {\n    if (event.target.closest('a')) return\n    const card = event.target.closest('.zhaizhai-reading-detail .zhaizhai-flip-card')\n    if (!card) return\n    if (flipSwitchTimer) {\n      clearTimeout(flipSwitchTimer)\n      flipSwitchTimer = null\n    }\n    const container = card.closest('.zhaizhai-reading-detail')\n    const cards = container ? container.querySelectorAll('.zhaizhai-flip-card.is-flipped') : []\n    const isFlipped = card.classList.contains('is-flipped')\n\n    cards.forEach(item => {\n      if (item !== card) item.classList.remove('is-flipped')\n    })\n\n    if (isFlipped) {\n      card.classList.remove('is-flipped')\n    } else {\n      const hasOtherFlipped = [...cards].some(item => item !== card)\n      if (hasOtherFlipped) {\n        // Close previous card first, then open target card for smoother switch.\n        flipSwitchTimer = setTimeout(() => {\n          card.classList.add('is-flipped')\n          flipSwitchTimer = null\n        }, 120)\n      } else {\n        card.classList.add('is-flipped')\n      }\n    }\n  })\n})()\n</script>\n</body></html>","raw":"---\ntitle: 菜根谭\ndate: 2026-05-21 08:12:03\ntype: page\naside: true\ncomments: false\n---\n\n> 共 3 条摘录，最近更新：2022-02-11\n\n<div class=\"zhaizhai-masonry zhaizhai-reading-detail\">\n<div class=\"shuoshuo-item zhaizhai-item \">\n  <div class=\"zhaizhai-flip-card\">\n    <div class=\"zhaizhai-face zhaizhai-face-front container\">\n      <div class=\"zhaizhai-top\">\n        <div class=\"zhaizhai-tags\"></div>\n        <time class=\"zhaizhai-date\">2018-11-08</time>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"zhaizhai-content-wrap\">\n        <div class=\"zhaizhai-content\">一念过差，<br>足丧生平之善；<br>终身检饬，<br>难盖一事之愆。</div>\n        <div class=\"zhaizhai-source\">—— 节选自《菜根谭》</div>\n        <div class=\"zhaizhai-meta\">\n          <span></span>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"zhaizhai-face zhaizhai-face-back container\">\n      <div class=\"zhaizhai-back-header\"><span class=\"zhaizhai-back-title\">思考卡片</span></div>\n      <div class=\"zhaizhai-back-body\"><section class=\"zhaizhai-back-section zhaizhai-back-empty\">暂无 insight</section></div>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"shuoshuo-item zhaizhai-item \">\n  <div class=\"zhaizhai-flip-card\">\n    <div class=\"zhaizhai-face zhaizhai-face-front container\">\n      <div class=\"zhaizhai-top\">\n        <div class=\"zhaizhai-tags\"></div>\n        <time class=\"zhaizhai-date\">2022-02-11</time>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"zhaizhai-content-wrap\">\n        <div class=\"zhaizhai-content\">君子好名，<br>便起欺人之念；<br>小人好名，<br>犹怀畏人之心。<br>故人而皆好名，<br>则开诈善之门。<br>使人而不好名，<br>则绝为善之路。<br>此讥好名者，<br>当严责君子，<br>不当过求于小人也。</div